headline: Hims & Hers Health Stock Stumbles After Earnings. Here’s Why.
summary: Hims & Hers Health  a telehealth platform that sells knockoffs of popular weight loss drugs, sank in after-hours trading after missing expectations on quarterly earnings and revenue.  The stock was down 12% at $55.68 in after-hours trading Monday.  It is up 162% so far this year, according to Dow Jones Market Data.
